items.title: Cats Showing Off Their Emotions According To Photographer

abcn:image.imagecaption:
The 29-year-old Philadelphia-based pet photographer and self proclaimed "crazy cat man" said: "This series on emotions is to disprove the stereotype that cats are cold and aloof.

"I want to show that cats are capable of a range of emotion, from serious to silly and everything in between."

The images are titled with the cat's name and what he believes they were feeling when the portrait was taken.
